overview: What started as a holiday craze in 1983 continues today with new Cabbage Patch Kids adopted everyday. Now those adorable Kids come to life in this special ‘one-of-a-kind’ collectors set featuring five musical adventures for you and your child to share. The stories help teach your children valuable lessons about friendship, teamwork, and just having fun!  Featuring 5 Musical Adventures: Saturday Night, The Clubhouse, The New Kid, The Screen Test, The Sing-Along
title: Cabbage Patch Kids: Collectors Set
